{"tid":1389062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布運動失敗","createTime":"2019-07-30T21:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T04:18:51.000Z","uid":98915,"like":11,"dislike":159,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"588d603b0daabf56a0fa0ac8c098bd8bf00480d4","tid":1389062,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:10:24.000Z","msg":"吹奏敵人 手足不能共患難 <br />\n義士做condom 互相分化<br />\n對暴力麻木 不斷打飛機自娛<br />\n睇嚟大家都生活得太安逸<br />\n未到地獄都唔會醒<br />\n<br />\n我哋成日笑支那人係奴才<br />\n香港人又何嘗唔係錢同女人嘅奴隸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大義？返工不了<br />\n俾班學生去做就啱<br />\n只要睇戲 收成果就夠<br />\n<br />\n其實香港一早已經死咗喺每個人嘅心<br />\n講幾多 睇幾多新聞 <br />\n都只不過係尋求一種自我救贖<br />\n<br />\n我知道又會有人話我散播失敗主義<br />\n請繼續分化<br />\n<br />\n心淡了 再見香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b6e636a80dbbe35051e34dc6c7dd1dd7c4cf94","tid":1389062,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb425affe289cc88ebd93833acafa5d44429fcd","tid":1389062,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:15:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「有片有證據」30/7 無勇武義士扮記者攻擊任何人，不要被分化</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388962\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推澄清"},{"pid":"de5dbe47f8e7fa1bf9c4666417ded80515c7b57c","tid":1389062,"uid":170944,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:21:08.000Z","msg":"個抗爭仲風風火火你卻係到淋冷水，唔係人地屈你散佈失敗主義丫，係你真係散佈緊丫，你灰心你放棄，你自己既選擇，但唔好出垃圾post傳染俾人。要走，請你快啲走，唔好阻住曬。"},{"pid":"cdc5024445760809bc19b2d04bd9c74124a59ec5","tid":1389062,"uid":98915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"de5dbe47f8e7fa1bf9c4666417ded80515c7b57c","tid":1389062,"uid":170944,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:21:08.000Z","msg":"